{"tid":1324962,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"賭博日記","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T17:21:44.000Z","uid":43215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e399b90c3e9d10711967bd52c6779e5e5fd39b66","tid":1324962,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"序章<br />\n<br />\n背景: 2019 年中開始 無業, 之前薪金20K per month, 25歲, 有女朋友 <br />\n<br />\n係仲未搵到野做之前, 想放手博一次; E段時間諗左好耐, 反正打一世工都無錢途<br />\n唔係我唔信自己做唔到manager, 中層管理人員, 係覺得做到又點? <br />\n<br />\n世界各國不斷印錢, 輸出通脹。其實以我一個中產家底既人泥講, 搵3萬同搵6-7萬可能個生活質素無乜太大分別, 唔會餓死, 亦唔會發達。<br />\n<br />\n加上我係一個比較低物慾既人而女朋友都唔係一個勁中意消費既人, 所以可以發下夢 - 做廢青有錢收<br />\n<br />\n當然, 依個夢可能今個星期輸哂, 無哂D錢就會完, 但反正我就要試一次<br />\n<br />\nE個post 係for 個人記錄, 除左日記外,會係度放下D關於投機/投資/賭博/概率既野<br />\n<br />\n剩餘資產: 11,400 , 月頭 5000蚊牛熊起家<br />\n而家會將5400 抽走去賭波, 留番6000 賭牛熊, 不過等緊個證券account 過完數<br />\n<br />\n希望趕得切係今個星期六賭波"},{"pid":"0b98498535dec1de3dc8a794f3bab2daae117cc2","tid":1324962,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szSznFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszSznFU.jpg&h=6b130983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2927996de7015fcbc0716dd6bccb9ce2b4569e5c","tid":1324962,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/va7znHp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fva7znHp.jpg&h=ee7e9e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B9AARAL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB9AARAL.jpg&h=c3bfcb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szdZyO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszdZyO6.jpg&h=ba8bd24d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"196cf6a88150a9f78d8e730de8e06700f94ef017","tid":1324962,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"個人好中意用條件交易, 但係E個位無啦啦比人殺左5格, <br />\n仲要個量比之前trade 既多 搞到個數細左<br />\n<br />\n以後個量大就最好避免比咁多格佢蝕"}]}